            <show chara="biankaDressShyClose" position="left" opacity="0.8"/>
            <show chara="ritaVestSquintClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="_Rita">噗。那么要准备洗个澡吗？需要搓背或者按摩的话，请不要客气哦。</speak>
