            <show chara="ShigureKiraSunGlassesConfidentClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="_ShigureKira">这一段路程差不多三公里，我们可以散步过去。没有问题吧？</speak>
            <show chara="ShigureKiraSunGlassesConfidentClose" position="left" opacity="0.8"/>
            <show chara="champoBlanketLaughClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="_Champollion">没有问题！</speak>
            <show chara="champoBlanketLaughClose" position="right" opacity="0.8"/>
            <show chara="ShigureKiraSunGlassesLaughClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="_ShigureKira">好，那我们出发吧！</speak>
