            <show chara="shakesCasualLaughClose" position="right" opacity="0.8"/>
            <show chara="biankaDressHesitateClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="_Bianka">……有吗？我觉得这就是个蛮普通的纪念碑吧？42大厦（Tower 42）难道不比它厉害无数倍吗？</speak>
            <show chara="biankaDressHesitateClose" position="left" opacity="0.8"/>
            <show chara="shakesCasualEmbarrassedClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="_Shakespeare">42号塔？是未来的什么神秘建筑吗？用来和外星人沟通的？</speak>
